{"tid":2169388,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《東方》及事主17度投訴律政司延誤檢控  辯方：X用盡言詞砌黎智英","createTime":"2020-08-22T12:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T13:06:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bbaa44ae7133939e0aa8a66c5cc50658df0a589f","tid":2169388,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/VHHZ6VRHM5EGPBEHEHIK3EJ2AU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FVHHZ6VRHM5EGPBEHEHIK3EJ2AU%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6TsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=23c49377\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FVHHZ6VRHM5EGPBEHEHIK3EJ2AU%2F&h=1ec3623c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/VHHZ6VRHM5EGPBEHEHIK3EJ2AU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《東方》及事主17度投訴律政司延誤檢控 <br />\n辯方：X用盡言詞砌黎智英<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hlZfVGOHBweDUqC_EoKXh41G1us=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YSM7WEUERBCMZA7YU32OZALWWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhlZfVGOHBweDUqC_EoKXh41G1us%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYSM7WEUERBCMZA7YU32OZALWWE.jpg&h=b254a625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■壹傳媒創辦人黎智英昨應訊後乘車離開。<br />\n<br />\n【刑恐記者案】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：精神科醫生：記者覆診甩底<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英2017年對追訪他的《東方日報》記者揚言「我實搞你」，被控刑事恐嚇一案昨續審。辯方指事主X報警只為黎添麻煩，滿足《東方》的目標，並提到《東方》和X曾17度去信律政司，投訴遲遲不起訴黎，姑息養奸，又謂愛國愛港媒體受打壓，反中亂港分子獲包庇，更質疑律政司與中央背道而馳，猶如反中亂港的保護傘，指X用盡一切言詞，務求令黎入罪。<br />\n<br />\n事主X稱2017年維園六四祈禱活動後遭恐嚇受驚，時間為晚上7時許。他承認。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指當晚維園有很多警察當值，但X返回辦公室與上司討論完才報警，問X報警是不。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英今年2月才被起訴，辯方問X和《東方日報》管理層是否非常不滿律政司遲遲不檢控。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i3wKrK0z9wE8uyCc0NOHoE5gYJA=/1155x1469/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B4T2JX3SMVB4ZOF2EH7EMEU7B4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi3wKrK0z9wE8uyCc0NOHoE5gYJA%3D%2F1155x1469%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB4T2JX3SMVB4ZOF2EH7EMEU7B4.gif&h=1e3f1579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n信中稱愛國愛港傳媒屢受打壓<br />\n<br />\nX承認自己和管理層的確不滿，並確認2018和2019年間，公司和他寫了17封信給律政司，投訴檢控延誤，他寫了其中13封。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指X想黎被控告和定罪，X稱「定唔定罪我唔知」，辯方續指他上庭就是希望黎入。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方讀出2018年10月致律政司信件，內容指《東方》為公義發聲，為民請命，愛國。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方再反對，指事主有權寫信申訴，毋須宣讀。辯方指X所思所說關乎他是否可信，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續問X曾在信函指控律政司說謊，有何根據，X稱「因為一路都唔處理我嗰件事」。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC965/20"},{"pid":"2ca08cfafd0fa3ad25e9425429aa5ef0ddcf166d","tid":2169388,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"唔係成個正苦都要造黎生咩"},{"pid":"7d1612697784a60ca79d824e1f7207f33129bd40","tid":2169388,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:00:43.000Z","msg":"on9到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceebf491fb75075a768239a80ae94c699563ede0","tid":2169388,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:06:17.000Z","msg":"鬧劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}